query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `max_pricing_periods` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `parkingLotId` int NOT NULL,
  `startHour` int NOT NULL,
  `endHour` int NOT NULL,
  `maxAmount` int NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()),
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `max_pricing_periods_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `max_pricing_periods_parkingLotId_parking_lots_id_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`parkingLotId`) REFERENCES `parking_lots`(`id`) ON DELETE cascade ON UPDATE no action
);
